@AccessControl.authorizationCheck: #NOT_REQUIRED
@EndUserText.label: 'Created Ledgers - Parts'
//@Metadata.ignorePropagatedAnnotations: true
define view entity zetr_ddl_i_created_ledger_part
  as select from zetr_t_oldef  as Parts
    inner join   I_CompanyCode as Company on Company.CompanyCode = Parts.bukrs
  association to parent zetr_ddl_i_created_ledger as _createdLedger on  $projection.bukrs = _createdLedger.bukrs
                                                                    and $projection.gjahr = _createdLedger.gjahr
                                                                    and $projection.monat = _createdLedger.monat
{
  key Parts.bukrs      as bukrs,
  key Parts.bcode      as bcode,
  key Parts.gjahr      as gjahr,
  key Parts.monat      as monat,
  key Parts.datbi      as datbi,
  key Parts.partn      as partn,
      Parts.parno      as parno,
      Parts.datab      as datab,
      Parts.tsfyd      as tsfyd,
      Parts.syevno     as syevno,
      Parts.eyevno     as eyevno,
      Parts.slinen     as slinen,
      Parts.elinen     as elinen,
      @Semantics.amount.currencyCode: 'waers'
      Parts.debit      as debit,
      @Semantics.amount.currencyCode: 'waers'
      Parts.credit     as credit,
      Parts.pdatab     as pdatab,
      Parts.pdatbi     as pdatbi,
      Parts.serok      as serok,
      Parts.yevok      as yevok,
      Parts.yvbok      as yvbok,
      Parts.kebok      as kebok,
      Parts.kbbok      as kbbok,
      Parts.gbyok      as gbyok,
      Parts.derok      as derok,
      Parts.gbkok      as gbkok,
      Parts.uiyev      as uiyev,
      Parts.uikeb      as uikeb,
      Parts.uider      as uider,
      Parts.fssyr      as fssyr,
      Parts.fseyr      as fseyr,
      Parts.ernam      as ernam,
      Parts.erdat      as erdat,
      Parts.erzet      as erzet,
      Parts.isyvk      as isyvk,
      Parts.igyvk      as igyvk,
      Parts.iskbk      as iskbk,
      Parts.igkbk      as igkbk,
      Parts.isgyk      as isgyk,
      Parts.iggyk      as iggyk,
      Parts.isgkk      as isgkk,
      Parts.iggkk      as iggkk,
      Parts.manup      as manup,
      Company.Currency as waers,
      _createdLedger // Make association public
}
